value.value: CREATE VIEW `hh_office`.`Client_Balances` as select c.id , min(s.session_date) as earliest , max(s.session_date) as latest , c.name as client_name , sum(v.charge) as charges , sum(v.client_paid) as client_paid , sum(v.insurance_paid) as insurance_paid , sum(v.due) as due from Client as c join Visit as v on v.Client_id = c.id join `Session` as s on v.Session_id = s.id group by c.id;
